PN,40601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783945155
OL,3,CMental health service failings
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,FWarning: This report contains details
OL,7,Fof self-harm and suicide.
OL,9,FAn inquest into the death of a 17-year-
OL,10,Fold who died in a mental health unit
OL,11,Ffor young people in Bristol has found
OL,12,Fthat failings from child and
OL,13,Fadolescent mental health services
OL,14,F"possibly contributed" to her death.
OL,16,FLucy Curtis died on 1 January 2024 at
OL,17,FRiverside Adolescent Unit at
OL,18,FBlackberry Hill Hospital in Bristol.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783945155
OL,3,CMental health service failings
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,FThe unit was under the care of Avon
OL,7,Fand Wiltshire Mental Health
OL,8,FPartnership NHS Trust (AWP). She had
OL,9,Fbeen admitted to the unit in December
OL,10,F2023.
OL,12,FAWP has since apologised to Lucy's
OL,13,Ffamily, admitting the service had
OL,14,F"failed" the teenager.
OL,16,FDelivering a narrative finding on
OL,17,FFriday, the jury at Avon Coroner's
OL,18,FCourt found delays in getting
OL,19,Fspecialist mental health support also
OL,20,F"possibly contributed" to the
OL,21,Fteenager's death.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783945155
OL,3,CMental health service failings
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,FThe jury found that the failures of
OL,7,Fthe unit to adhere to Lucy's
OL,8,Fobservation levels on the morning of
OL,9,Fher death and the time lost before
OL,10,Femergency treatment started also
OL,11,F"possibly contributed" to her death.
OL,13,FBefore her admission to the Riverside
OL,14,FUnit, Lucy had previously been an
OL,15,Finpatient on a mental health ward at
OL,16,FWessex House, under the care of
OL,17,FSomerset NHS Foundation Trust. She had
OL,18,Fadmitted herself voluntarily to that
OL,19,Funit.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783945155
OL,3,CMental health service failings
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,FThe inquest heard that while Lucy was
OL,7,Fat that unit, her self-harm escalated.
OL,9,FBefore that, she had spent a period
OL,10,Funder the care of her GP, where she
OL,11,Fcame into contact with Children and
OL,12,FAdolescent Mental Health Services
OL,13,F(CAMHS) in the community.
OL,15,FLucy's parents, Michelle Curtis and
OL,16,FBarry Curtis, say they first became
OL,17,Fconcerned about Lucy's mental health
OL,18,Fwhen she was at sixth form in 2023 and
OL,19,Fwas made aware by the school that she
OL,20,Fstruggling.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783945155
OL,3,CMental health service failings
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,FLucy had been to the GP in January
OL,7,F2023 and the doctor made a referral to
OL,8,FCAMHS who ruled that she didn't meet
OL,9,Fthe criteria for the service.
OL,11,FMs Curtis says her daughter, who they
OL,12,Fdescribe as "kind" and "fiercely
OL,13,Floyal", deteriorated quite "rapidly"
OL,14,Fthroughout that year.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783945155
OL,3,CMental health service failings
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,F"She was doing everything that we
OL,7,Fteach young people to do - she was
OL,8,Fhonest about her struggles, reaching
OL,9,Fout and talking to school staff about
OL,10,Fwhat was happening - those staff were
OL,11,Fsupporting Lucy to go to the GP to
OL,12,Faccess services".
OL,14,FThey say that the CAMHS team believed
OL,15,Fshe was at "low risk of acting on her
OL,16,Fsuicidal thoughts", so she didn't
OL,17,F"meet the criteria for the service".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783945155
OL,3,CMental health service failings
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,FThe CAMHS team advised that if her low
OL,7,Fmood continued, she should go to the
OL,8,FGP to get antidepressant medication
OL,9,Fand consider private counselling.
OL,11,FIf you are struggling there is help
OL,12,Favailable. For links to support and
OL,13,Fhelp click here.
OL,15,FMs Curtis describes the "distressing"
OL,16,Fsituation for Lucy where the family
OL,17,Fwere going back and forth between the
OL,18,FGP and CAMHS to figure out who was
OL,19,Fable to prescribe medication for a
OL,20,Fchild.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783945155
OL,3,CMental health service failings
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,FThey say CAMHS only started "engaging"
OL,7,Fwith Lucy in early August 2023, by
OL,8,Fwhich point "she was actively
OL,9,Fsuicidal".
OL,11,FHer father says "there was no service
OL,12,Fto stop her getting to the point of
OL,13,Fcrisis".
OL,15,FMs Curtis says: "We wonder if she had
OL,16,Fthat support sooner, whether that
OL,17,Fwould have prevented her getting to a
OL,18,Fpoint where she needed to be admitted
OL,19,Fto hospital".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783945155
OL,3,CMental health service failings
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,FMr Curtis says there is a need for in-
OL,7,Fpatient CAMHS wards, which Bristol
OL,8,Fdoesn't currently have.
OL,10,FAWP temporarily closed the Riverside
OL,11,FAdolescent Unit on 24 January 2024
OL,12,Fafter internal reviews found it "did
OL,13,Fnot provide assurance that the Unit
OL,14,Fcould consistently deliver a safe
OL,15,Flevel of care moving forward".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783945155
OL,3,CMental health service failings
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,FA statement from Avon and Wiltshire
OL,7,FMental Health Partnership NHS Trust
OL,8,Freads: "We are deeply sorry for the
OL,9,Ffailures in Lucy's care that
OL,10,Fcontributed to her death. Lucy should
OL,11,Fhave been safe in our care, and we
OL,12,Ffailed in that duty. We accept the
OL,13,Finquest's conclusions in full.
OL,15,F"Our thoughts remain with Lucy's
OL,16,Ffamily and loved ones, and we
OL,17,Fapologise directly to them. We
OL,18,Facknowledge the strength and dignity
OL,19,Fthey have shown and will offer any
OL,20,Fsupport they need.
OL,26,@pD@HOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783945155
OL,3,CMental health service failings
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,F"We are committed to embedding and
OL,7,Fsustaining the changes identified
OL,8,Fthrough the reviews that have taken
OL,9,Fplace. Following Lucy's death, the
OL,10,FRiverside Unit was closed temporarily
OL,11,Fand remains so. We are assessing
OL,12,Foptions for a new inpatient CAMHS
OL,13,Funit, and the lessons from Lucy's
OL,14,Fdeath will be central to its design.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783945155
OL,3,CMental health service failings
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,F"We also acknowledge that Lucy's care
OL,7,Facross the wider CAMHS pathway before
OL,8,Fher admission to Riverside fell short
OL,9,Fof the standards she and her family
OL,10,Fdeserved, and we continue working with
OL,11,Fpartners to ensure safe, effective
OL,12,Fservices for local young people."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@aO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783945155
OL,3,CMental health service failings
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,FDr Sathya Cherukuri, associate medical
OL,7,Fdirector for mental health and
OL,8,Flearning disabilities at Somerset NHS
OL,9,FFoundation Trust, said: "We extend our
OL,10,Fdeepest sympathies to Lucy's family.
OL,11,FWe did not engage with Lucy and her
OL,12,Ffamily in the way that we should have
OL,13,Fabout her care, and we apologise
OL,14,Fwholeheartedly for this.
OL,26,@qD@YOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1783945155
OL,3,CMental health service failings
OL,4,C'possibly contributed' to girl's death
OL,6,F"We are working hard to address the
OL,7,Fpoints the coroner raised. We are
OL,8,Fcommitted to the Triangle of Care
OL,9,Fprogramme, which involves
OL,10,Fstrengthening our communication and
OL,11,Finformation-sharing with patients,
OL,12,Ffamilies and carers, helping to ensure
OL,13,Fthey are appropriately involved in
OL,14,Fboth care and discharge planning.
OL,16,F"This work supports our commitment to
OL,17,Fproviding safe, person-centred care
OL,18,Fand ensuring that people feel
OL,19,Finformed, listened to and supported
OL,20,Fthroughout their time in our care."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
